  m_text: "Tr\xE2u g\xE1c b\u1EBFp is a preserved buffalo meat specialty from the
    mountainous regions of Northern Vietnam, especially among ethnic minority communities.
    The meat is stored above the kitchen fireplace for long periods. It was traditionally
    made to preserve food during colder seasons and long trips. Common seasonings
    include m\u1EAFc kh\xE9n, chili, ginger, and forest herbs. \n"
